"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?27/24/28035?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Insomnia treatments (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"    </p>",
"    <p class=\"headingAnchor2\" id=\"H21\">",
"     <span class=\"h2\">",
